User Stories - IS

Actor: Teacher
Feature: Shared documents updating live 
Rationale: Allow pupils to all contribute to a class group assignment

Actor:  Student
Feature: Upload Media to Documents
Rationale: Allows me to build a lab report with appropriate images

Actor: Student 
Feature: Emojis + Scribble features
Rationale: Allows me to take a break from shared report writing to doodle on the page

Actor: Party Planner 
Feature: Password Protection
Rationale: Allows me to keep keep a surprise party plan only in the hands of those with the key

Actor:  Student Mentor
Feature: Comments
Rationale: I use comments so that when I check in to see my students work I can leave notes for
	   them to read. 